OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with light and patchy rain,
OL,7,Fthe rain turning showery through the
OL,8,Fnight and turning occasionally heavy
OL,9,Fin the west. Strengthening
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds with risk of
OL,11,Fcoastal gales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FRain spreading southeast in
OL,14,Fthe morning, heavy initially in the
OL,15,Fwest but lighter in the east. Then
OL,16,Fturning drier and brighter with just a
OL,17,Ffew light showers. Strong winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
