OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FQuite
OL,6,Fcloudy with a few showers Sunday
OL,7,Fmorning, turning dry and bright
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon. Fairly
OL,9,Funsettled and changeable Monday and
OL,10,FTuesday with rain or showers at times.
